OL,3,CNewcastle's Clean Air Zone: One year on
OL,5,FOne year on from the introduction of
OL,6,FNewcastle's Clean Air Zone (CAZ) the
OL,7,Fimpact of the toll is yet to be
OL,8,Fassessed.
OL,10,FWhile some are in favour of the
OL,11,Fcharges, which were introduced in the
OL,12,Fcity centre last January, others say
OL,13,Fit is targeting the wrong type of
OL,14,Fdrivers.
OL,16,FBrought in with the aim of driving
OL,17,Fdown illegal levels of air pollution,
OL,18,Fit originally imposed penalties on
OL,19,Folder buses, coaches, taxis and
OL,20,Florries before being extended to cover
OL,21,Fvans in July.
