OL,3,CNewcastle's Clean Air Zone: One year on
OL,5,FLike in other clean air zones in
OL,6,Fcities across the country, the
OL,7,Fvehicles that fall foul of the
OL,8,Fenvironmental regulations are charged
OL,9,Fa toll or face a fine if they do not
OL,10,Fpay.
OL,12,FNewcastle City Council, which has
OL,13,Fcollected #2million in tolls and fines
OL,14,Fover the last 12 months, says less
OL,15,Fthan 1% of vehicles entering the city
OL,16,Fcentre since its introduction have
OL,17,Fpaid the charges.
OL,19,FThe latest figures, which run up to 31
OL,20,FDecember 2023, show that:
