OL,3,CNewcastle's Clean Air Zone: One year on
OL,5,FThe CAZ was introduced in response to
OL,6,Fa Government order for local councils
OL,7,Fto reduce air level pollution.
OL,9,FNo official data has yet been
OL,10,Fpublished assessing how successful it
OL,11,Fhas been.
OL,13,FHowever, Professor Anil Namdeo, of
OL,14,FNorthumbria University, said his own
OL,15,Fdata has shown it has made a
OL,16,Fdifference.
OL,18,FHe said: "The data for the civic
OL,19,Fcentre, where most of the buses come,
OL,20,Fthe reduction is 32%. That's a big
OL,21,Fdrop."
