OL,3,CNewcastle's Clean Air Zone: One year on
OL,5,FNewcastle City Council has a fund
OL,6,Favailable for grants to help those
OL,7,Fwith non-compliant vehicles to upgrade
OL,8,Fthem.
OL,10,FSince they became available, there
OL,11,Fhave been 3,597 applications, of which
OL,12,F1,298 approved. The council said 668
OL,13,Fvehicles had been upgraded.
