OL,3,CNewcastle's Clean Air Zone: One year on
OL,5,FA spokesperson for Newcastle and
OL,6,FGateshead Clean Air Zone said: "The
OL,7,Faim of the Clean Air Zone is to reduce
OL,8,Fharmful air pollution by encouraging
OL,9,Fthe use of cleaner vehicles and, as
OL,10,Fpart of the scheme, grant funding
OL,11,Ftowards the cost of newer vehicles has
OL,12,Fbeen helping people to upgrade and
OL,13,Freplace their older, more polluting
OL,14,Fvehicles.
OL,16,F"We have approved grant funding worth
OL,17,Fover #5m and, one year on from the
OL,18,Flaunch of the zone, we are beginning
OL,19,Fto see a gradual decrease in the
OL,20,Fnumber of non-compliant vehicles
OL,21,Fentering the zone.
