OL,5,F"We will continue to monitor pollution
OL,6,Fdata and expect to be able to see
OL,7,Fevidence of the impact of the CAZ once
OL,8,Fthe annual average data for 2023
OL,9,Fbecomes available later this year.
OL,11,F"The Clean Air Zone was introduced in
OL,12,Fresponse to a legal order from
OL,13,Fgovernment that required Newcastle and
OL,14,FGateshead councils take action to
OL,15,Faddress illegal levels of pollution in
OL,16,Fcertain areas.
