OL,3,CNewcastle's Clean Air Zone: One year on
OL,5,F"The impact of poor air quality on
OL,6,Fpeople's health ` particularly
OL,7,Fchildren and those living with chronic
OL,8,Fhealth conditions ` is well documented
OL,9,Fand we remain committed to tackling
OL,10,Fthis."
OL,12,FLoree Moran-Wilson, from Kenton Food
OL,13,FBank, is among those to have been able
OL,14,Fto upgrade her van after the toll was
OL,15,Fintroduced.
OL,17,FShe said: "With regards to what I do
OL,18,Fon a day-to-day basis I don't think it
OL,19,Fneeded to be as complicated as it has
OL,20,Fbeen. It took four-and-a-half months
OL,21,Fto get a CAZ-compliant van.
